bio: Laguna Candles is a black women-owned, family run business founded by Sharie Hendricks, a passionate candle lover and entrepreneur.  Laguna Candles utilizes a proprietary coconut, wax blend and all candles are lovingly, hand-poured and hand-crafted in the Laguna Beach, California Facility. Our candles are sustainable, ecologically-sound & pesticide-free.  No animal testing, Phthalates, parabens and sulfate free,100% unbleached cotton wicks. Unparalleled fragrance integrity, and we adhere to the highest quality & regulatory standards. Each elegantly rich, fragrance has been designed in collaboration with a master perfumer.  Choose from our robust scent library or formulate your own unique scent from scratch.
